Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里  和池  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是火炬？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对
